FIRST CALIFORNIA BANK
v.
McDONALD. No. S222858. Supreme Court of California March 9, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, and CUÉLLAR, JJ., concur.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 5. Review in the above-captioned matter is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b).)

KRUGER, J., was absent and did not participate.
